videos.description: Chevez Goodwin grabs the offensive rebound and rocks the rim with a big slam, then muscles home a bucket through contact on the next possession.
videos.headline: Wofford's Goodwin jams, gets and-1 on back-to-back possessions

videos.description: Fletcher Magee pulls up from beyond the arc to knock down a triple and send the Terriers into halftime with a double-digit lead on the Keydets.
videos.headline: Magee hits 3-ball to beat 1st-half buzzer for Wofford
